            <p><span class="Header">Online ITIL <font color="#0066CC">Planning Protection and Optimization</font> Training Model</span></p>
             
              <ul>
              <li><b>Service Operation course material includes:</b><br /><br />
              	<ol>
                <li><span class="SubHeader">Learning through the Study guides</span> - Twelve hours</li>
               <li>	<span class="SubHeader">Practice through Exercises:</span><br /><br />
